WEBVTT

00:06:57.887 --> 00:07:00.583
by the traditional banking industry.

00:07:00.607 --> 00:07:03.216
How do we make sure that those people

00:07:03.240 --> 00:07:05.006
have that opportunity?

00:07:05.030 --> 00:07:06.952
And it feels like a smartphone

00:07:06.976 --> 00:07:09.188
becomes an essential item.

00:07:09.212 --> 00:07:11.192
How do we address that?

00:07:12.158 --> 00:07:13.477
DS: Yeah.

00:07:13.501 --> 00:07:20.380
I do think that a mobile
is really a key to unlocking this.

00:07:20.796 --> 00:07:23.731
I've often said that, really,

00:07:23.755 --> 00:07:28.570
one of the big moon shots
for the financial services industry

00:07:28.594 --> 00:07:31.716
is this idea of not just
financial inclusion.